cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.DS 

The paper proposes a novel method for task decomposition in reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The method is designed to improve learning speed and generalization, which are important considerations in robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY). The proposed method also leverages association rule mining, which is a technique commonly used in data mining and machine learning (cs.DS).
